+|---------|--------|
+| brew | `brew upgrade ivankuznetsov/hive/hive` |
+| aur | `yay -Syu hive-bin` (or paru) |
+| bash | re-run official `install.sh` |
+| dev / unknown | print instructions; non-zero exit |
+
+`--check` reports current vs latest GitHub release tag without applying.
