@@ -0,0 +1,32 @@
+---
+title: Hive::ServiceInstaller
+type: module
+source: lib/hive/service_installer.rb
+created: 2026-07-10
+updated: 2026-07-10
+tags: [packaging, daemon, systemd, launchd]
+---
+
+**TLDR**: Installs or removes user-level systemd / launchd units for `hive daemon`. Bodies come from `share/hive/services/*/*.erb` templates so packaged samples and runtime install stay aligned.
+
+## Modes
+
+| Mode | Behavior |
+|------|----------|
+| `:enable_start` | Write unit, enable and start (systemd `enable --now`; launchd `bootstrap` + `kickstart`) |
+| `:register_only` | Write unit only. launchd sets `RunAtLoad=false` and `Disabled=true` so login does not auto-start |
