+## launchd notes
+
+- Prefer `launchctl bootstrap` / `bootout` when available; fall back to `load` / `unload`.
+- Command failures surface on stderr and raise `Hive::Error` (no silent ignore).
+- Enable later after register-only: `launchctl enable gui/$UID/local.hive-daemon` then `launchctl bootstrap gui/$UID ~/Library/LaunchAgents/local.hive-daemon.plist`.
